SetTokenFactor(address,(uint16,uint16,ui.notice: The governor sets oracle token factor for a token.

SetWhitelist(address,bool).notice: The governor sets token whitelist for an ERC1155 token.

UnsetTokenFactor(address).notice: The governor unsets oracle token factor for a token.

acceptGovernor().details: Accept to become the new governor. Must be called by the pending governor.

asCELOBorrow(address,uint256,address).details: Return the value of the given input as CELO for borrow purpose.

params.amount: ERC20 token amount to get borrow value
params.owner: Token owner address (currently unused by this implementation)
params.token: ERC20 token address to get borrow value

asCELOCollateral(address,uint256,uint256.details: Return the value of the given input as CELO for collateral purpose.

params.amount: Token amount to get collateral value
params.id: ERC1155 token id to get collateral value
params.owner: Token owner address (currently unused by this implementation)
params.token: ERC1155 token address to get collateral value

constructor.details: Create the contract and initialize the first governor.

convertForLiquidation(address,address,ui.details: Return the amount of token out as liquidation reward for liquidating token in.

setPendingGovernor(address).details: Set the pending governor, which will be the governor once accepted.

params._pendingGovernor: The address to become the pending governor.

setTokenFactors(address[],(uint16,uint16.details: Set oracle token factors for the given list of token addresses.

params.tokens: List of tokens to set info

setWhitelistERC1155(address[],bool).details: Set whitelist status for the given list of token addresses.

params.tokens: List of tokens to set whitelist status

support(address).details: Return whether the ERC20 token is supported

params.token: The ERC20 token to check for support

supportWrappedToken(address,uint256).details: Return whether the oracle supports evaluating collateral value of the given token.

params.id: ERC1155 token id to check for support
params.token: ERC1155 token address to check for support
